  "concept": "vuejs/core#12827: `TransitionGroup` causes hydration mismatch with `tag` fallthrough prop in SSR",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:21:19.631002+00:00",
  "text": "`TransitionGroup` causes hydration mismatch with `tag` fallthrough prop in SSR\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.5.13\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#__SSR__\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nSee in link.\n\n### What is expected?\n\nRender tag as CSR.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nTag is not rendered.\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\n\n```\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "scope: ssr",
    "has workaround",
    "🔩 p2-edge-case"
  ],
